  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2682960/extras/588bd7dc54cf6dccba80dc8744511e0d.poster.avif?t=1701520861\" width=600 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2682960/extras/588bd7dc54cf6dccba80dc8744511e0d.webm?t=1701520861\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2682960/extras/588bd7dc54cf6dccba80dc8744511e0d.mp4?t=1701520861\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Super Cave Run is a 2D, pixel art platform game, inspired by classic platforms and with a slightly high difficulty.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >HISTORY</h2>Hat Man worked on an excavation when he fell into a hole and now he needs your help to escape this prison.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >ENVIRONMENT</h2>The game features an environment with fixed and breakable platforms, fireballs, traps and much more.<br> At times you will need to rely on your skill, at others, patience and speed.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >CHALLENGE</h2>Your biggest challenge is to save our friend so he can return home.<br> Lose your patience, peace and tranquility by avoiding saving him from the most dangerous cave in the world.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2682960/extras/fd171a9ee7644ec07b4c7a9328f68260.avif?t=1701520861\" width=600 height=219 /></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2682960/extras/588bd7dc54cf6dccba80dc8744511e0d.poster.avif?t=1701520861\" width=600 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2682960/extras/588bd7dc54cf6dccba80dc8744511e0d.webm?t=1701520861\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2682960/extras/588bd7dc54cf6dccba80dc8744511e0d.mp4?t=1701520861\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Super Cave Run is a 2D, pixel art platform game, inspired by classic platforms and with a slightly high difficulty.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >HISTORY</h2>Hat Man worked on an excavation when he fell into a hole and now he needs your help to escape this prison.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >ENVIRONMENT</h2>The game features an environment with fixed and breakable platforms, fireballs, traps and much more.<br> At times you will need to rely on your skill, at others, patience and speed.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >CHALLENGE</h2>Your biggest challenge is to save our friend so he can return home.<br> Lose your patience, peace and tranquility by avoiding saving him from the most dangerous cave in the world.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2682960/extras/fd171a9ee7644ec07b4c7a9328f68260.avif?t=1701520861\" width=600 height=219 /></span>",
